1
00:01:29,980 --> 00:01:34,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<font face="Times New Roman"><font color="#292c35">Episode 9</font></font></font>

2
00:01:29,980 --> 00:01:34,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<font face="Times New Roman"><font color="#292c35">"Judge's Problem"</font></font></font>

3
00:01:37,700 --> 00:01:39,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, he's closed.</font>

4
00:01:39,660 --> 00:01:42,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Even he goes out sometimes.</font>

5
00:01:45,090 --> 00:01:46,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Mr. Lizel!</font>

6
00:01:46,400 --> 00:01:48,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm so sorry. I'll open 
the shop right away.</font>

7
00:01:48,930 --> 00:01:52,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's all right. We just arrived.</font>

8
00:01:52,590 --> 00:01:54,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Could you appraise something for me?</font>

9
00:01:55,070 --> 00:01:57,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, come in.</font>

10
00:02:05,290 --> 00:02:06,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Judge?</font>

11
00:02:06,300 --> 00:02:07,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Y-Yes?</font>

12
00:02:07,730 --> 00:02:09,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Did something happen?</font>

13
00:02:11,250 --> 00:02:12,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, um...</font>

14
00:02:16,660 --> 00:02:18,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's nothing.</font>

15
00:02:24,920 --> 00:02:28,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Um, thank you.</font>

16
00:02:28,130 --> 00:02:29,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll be back.</font>

17
00:02:32,430 --> 00:02:35,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It wasn't those bandits.</font>

18
00:02:40,370 --> 00:02:42,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can't. I'm leaving.</font>

19
00:02:42,730 --> 00:02:46,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He wouldn't pull something after 
being terrified that badly.</font>

20
00:02:46,700 --> 00:02:49,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He did cry until his eyelids were puffy.</font>

21
00:02:55,810 --> 00:02:57,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you going to help?</font>

22
00:02:58,440 --> 00:03:00,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">For now, I'll wait and see.</font>

23
00:03:00,660 --> 00:03:04,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He didn't complain, so he probably 
doesn't want to be cheered up.</font>

24
00:03:04,820 --> 00:03:07,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Something must've happened to his shop.</font>

25
00:03:07,780 --> 00:03:11,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's not something we can butt into.</font>

26
00:03:11,350 --> 00:03:13,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is that right?</font>

27
00:03:13,050 --> 00:03:15,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's what it means 
to be a professional.</font>

28
00:03:16,290 --> 00:03:18,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Welcome back.</font>

29
00:03:22,490 --> 00:03:26,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I wasn't expecting you to come 
today after yesterday's events.</font>

30
00:03:26,130 --> 00:03:28,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Really? Nice.</font>

31
00:03:28,420 --> 00:03:30,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Has your wrist healed already?</font>

32
00:03:30,410 --> 00:03:33,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's totally fine. 
I've got healing potions.</font>

33
00:03:33,360 --> 00:03:38,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Mr. Lizel, you're not being bothered 
by nasty men again, are you?</font>

34
00:03:38,510 --> 00:03:40,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're not far from the mark.</font>

35
00:03:40,480 --> 00:03:41,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, wait!</font>

36
00:03:41,470 --> 00:03:45,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">See? You shouldn't lie 
about knowing Mr. Lizel.</font>

37
00:03:45,700 --> 00:03:48,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Gil, do you mind if I 
take a shower first?</font>

38
00:03:48,150 --> 00:03:48,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Go ahead.</font>

39
00:03:48,290 --> 00:03:49,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're leaving me here?</font>

40
00:03:49,660 --> 00:03:54,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wait, seriously?
Let me join your party...</font>

41
00:03:55,120 --> 00:03:57,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He's actually leaving!</font>

42
00:03:57,580 --> 00:04:01,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Come on, don't squat there.</font>

43
00:04:01,100 --> 00:04:03,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your hair's brushing the floor.</font>

44
00:04:04,050 --> 00:04:06,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You think he hates me?</font>

45
00:04:07,160 --> 00:04:12,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Mr. Lizel wouldn't bother hating 
someone who doesn't matter.</font>

46
00:04:12,100 --> 00:04:13,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't matter?!</font>

47
00:04:17,740 --> 00:04:21,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Okay, I'm staying here, too. 
Got any rooms?</font>

48
00:04:21,030 --> 00:04:22,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We're full.</font>

49
00:04:22,100 --> 00:04:24,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Can't you do something about that?</font>

50
00:04:23,480 --> 00:04:25,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No!</font>

51
00:04:26,540 --> 00:04:29,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So you're finally willing to talk to me.</font>

52
00:04:29,650 --> 00:04:32,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The innkeeper seemed put out.</font>

53
00:04:32,360 --> 00:04:35,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Anyway, you had something 
to discuss, didn't you?</font>

54
00:04:35,390 --> 00:04:39,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I came to ask to join your party. 
Is the answer still no?</font>

55
00:04:39,820 --> 00:04:40,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes.</font>

56
00:04:41,260 --> 00:04:45,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>He's not responding like before, so...</i></font>

57
00:04:45,490 --> 00:04:49,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I promise I won't hurt you again.</font>

58
00:04:49,420 --> 00:04:52,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's all right. I don't think you will.</font>

59
00:04:54,170 --> 00:04:56,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Then what am I supposed to do?</font>

60
00:04:56,150 --> 00:05:01,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'd like to see you sell yourself 
in a way only you can.</font>

61
00:05:03,150 --> 00:05:04,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Okay, then a bribe.</font>

62
00:05:04,940 --> 00:05:10,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The item shop you're friendly with fought 
with the merchant's guild today.</font>

63
00:05:10,790 --> 00:05:13,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's a good bribe.
One that doesn't leave evidence.</font>

64
00:05:13,620 --> 00:05:14,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Right?</font>

65
00:05:14,990 --> 00:05:17,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But how did you learn that?</font>

66
00:05:17,600 --> 00:05:21,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'd been investigating you 
recently, so as part of that.</font>

67
00:05:21,060 --> 00:05:25,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, I see. Gil seemed annoyed 
about someone watching us.</font>

68
00:05:25,890 --> 00:05:31,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Seriously? I actually used 
decent guys this time.</font>

69
00:05:32,930 --> 00:05:34,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're not mad?</font>

70
00:05:35,360 --> 00:05:37,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Were you watching me, too?</font>

71
00:05:37,430 --> 00:05:38,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You couldn't tell?</font>

72
00:05:40,270 --> 00:05:41,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Not at all.</font>

73
00:05:43,500 --> 00:05:47,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's not as though you did 
anything to me. I'm not mad.</font>

74
00:05:47,830 --> 00:05:49,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's good.</font>

75
00:05:49,700 --> 00:05:52,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So, about Judge...</font>

76
00:05:53,080 --> 00:05:55,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, right.</font>

77
00:05:55,110 --> 00:06:00,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A few of his labyrinth items were 
stolen by an employee he hired.</font>

78
00:06:00,500 --> 00:06:08,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<font color="#fefefe">m 0 0 l 230 0 l 230 215 l 0 215</font></font>

79
00:06:00,500 --> 00:06:08,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font color="#303030"><font size="22">Merchant's Guild</font></font></font>

80
00:06:00,500 --> 00:06:08,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<font color="#fefefe">m 0 0 l 230 0 l 230 215 l 0 215</font></font>

81
00:06:00,500 --> 00:06:08,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font color="#303030"><font size="16">Merchant</font></font></font>

82
00:06:00,870 --> 00:06:04,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">At a registered merchant's request,</font>

83
00:06:02,170 --> 00:06:08,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<font color="#fefefe">m 0 0 l 230 0 l 230 215 l 0 215</font></font>

84
00:06:02,170 --> 00:06:08,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font color="#303030"><font size="14">{\an7}I'd like to leave my
shop for a while, but
I have no one to
watch the store…</font></font></font>

85
00:06:03,090 --> 00:06:08,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<font color="#fefefe">m 0 0 l 230 0 l 230 215 l 0 215</font></font>

86
00:06:03,090 --> 00:06:08,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font color="#303030"><font size="16">Submit
Request</font></font></font>

87
00:06:04,440 --> 00:06:08,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">the guild dispatches staff, 
like shopkeepers.</font>

88
00:06:04,590 --> 00:06:08,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<font color="#fefefe">m 0 0 l 230 0 l 230 215 l 0 215</font></font>

89
00:06:04,590 --> 00:06:08,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font color="#303030"><font size="25">Dispatch Staff</font></font></font>

90
00:06:08,940 --> 00:06:13,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The employee was a high-ranking staff 
member dispatched by the guild,</font>

91
00:06:13,720 --> 00:06:15,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">so the fight got really nasty.</font>

92
00:06:16,390 --> 00:06:21,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I see. The staff denied 
they stole anything.</font>

93
00:06:21,220 --> 00:06:25,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Not wanting to admit their mistake, 
the guild believed their staff</font>

94
00:06:25,720 --> 00:06:28,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and is treating Judge like a liar.</font>

95
00:06:28,270 --> 00:06:29,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Exactly.</font>

96
00:06:30,550 --> 00:06:36,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>The guild's higher-ups would know 
that Judge is Mr. Insigh's grandson.</i></font>

97
00:06:36,110 --> 00:06:38,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Perhaps he's dealing with 
lower-level members.</i></font>

98
00:06:39,220 --> 00:06:44,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>It's not my place to talk to the 
merchant's guild, so what should I do?</i></font>

99
00:06:46,260 --> 00:06:48,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Pretty useful, right?</font>

100
00:06:49,000 --> 00:06:51,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Aren't you a bandit leader?</font>

101
00:06:51,590 --> 00:06:54,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'd like to avoid having 
you join my party.</font>

102
00:06:54,720 --> 00:06:56,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Then I'll quit being a bandit.</font>

103
00:06:56,600 --> 00:07:00,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A bandit gang without a 
leader would sow chaos.</font>

104
00:07:00,620 --> 00:07:03,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh. Should I kill them all, then?</font>

105
00:07:03,490 --> 00:07:05,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It would be disastrous if you failed.</font>

106
00:07:05,830 --> 00:07:07,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Poisoning them might work.</font>

107
00:07:07,840 --> 00:07:11,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">As a snake beastman, 
you'd be the prime suspect.</font>

108
00:07:11,590 --> 00:07:16,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If a bandit gang as large as yours 
were wiped out, it'd be big news.</font>

109
00:07:18,520 --> 00:07:20,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you actually worried about me?</font>

110
00:07:21,460 --> 00:07:22,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Of course.</font>

111
00:07:25,110 --> 00:07:28,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">By the way, you can poison people?</font>

112
00:07:28,000 --> 00:07:30,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh? Yeah, it's easy.</font>

113
00:07:30,910 --> 00:07:35,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You secrete poison from glands 
inside your mouth, was it?</font>

114
00:07:36,820 --> 00:07:39,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'd rather not say, but...</font>

115
00:07:44,510 --> 00:07:45,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Open your mouth.</font>

116
00:07:49,320 --> 00:07:51,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If you want to know that badly, go ahead.</font>

117
00:07:51,660 --> 00:07:54,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">In exchange, let me join your party.</font>

118
00:07:57,650 --> 00:08:00,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The glands are behind your fangs, so...</font>

119
00:08:00,730 --> 00:08:02,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A slit at the base.</font>

120
00:08:02,850 --> 00:08:04,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is this the gland?</font>

121
00:08:04,690 --> 00:08:05,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">'eah.</font>

122
00:08:06,030 --> 00:08:08,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Could you secrete something now?</font>

123
00:08:12,960 --> 00:08:14,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What are you doing?!</font>

124
00:08:15,670 --> 00:08:17,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I was curious what kind of poison it was.</font>

125
00:08:18,530 --> 00:08:21,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">My mouth and fingertip feel a bit numb.</font>

126
00:08:21,550 --> 00:08:24,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, yeah! It's an anesthetic poison!</font>

127
00:08:24,370 --> 00:08:25,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Aw, man.</font>

128
00:08:25,660 --> 00:08:26,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Drink this.</font>

129
00:08:31,370 --> 00:08:35,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why do potions have to taste like 
they make everything worse?</font>

130
00:08:35,870 --> 00:08:37,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't believe you.</font>

131
00:08:37,670 --> 00:08:39,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What if it killed you instantly?</font>

132
00:08:44,060 --> 00:08:46,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm fine now.</font>

133
00:08:47,330 --> 00:08:49,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Seriously?</font>

134
00:08:49,140 --> 00:08:51,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Were you worried about me?</font>

135
00:08:51,120 --> 00:08:52,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I mean—</font>

136
00:08:52,490 --> 00:08:58,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Didn't you promise to 
never hurt me again?</font>

137
00:08:59,470 --> 00:09:01,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Did he actually believe that?</i></font>

138
00:09:07,340 --> 00:09:11,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, Blade! Hey!</font>

139
00:09:11,610 --> 00:09:13,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Stop knocking. It's loud.</font>

140
00:09:13,580 --> 00:09:16,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What did you teach that guy?</font>

141
00:09:16,240 --> 00:09:19,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nobody tastes something 
they know is poison.</font>

142
00:09:19,650 --> 00:09:21,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't yell at me to hide 
your embarrassment.</font>

143
00:09:21,540 --> 00:09:23,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What? I'm not embarrassed.</font>

144
00:09:26,380 --> 00:09:27,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't close the door!</font>

145
00:09:27,850 --> 00:09:30,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's talk about what 
you're teaching him!</font>

146
00:09:30,460 --> 00:09:34,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, open up! Open this 
door! Open the door!</font>

147
00:09:34,300 --> 00:09:36,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I might get in trouble with Gil later.</font>

148
00:09:38,110 --> 00:09:40,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">All the stolen items are labyrinth goods,</font>

149
00:09:41,180 --> 00:09:43,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">all worth around one gold.</font>

150
00:09:43,660 --> 00:09:45,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Where'd you learn that?</font>

151
00:09:46,230 --> 00:09:49,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Total coincidence.</font>

152
00:09:49,200 --> 00:09:53,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I was looking for something juicy to 
bring you and happened to stumble upon it.</font>

153
00:09:53,490 --> 00:09:55,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How kind of you.</font>

154
00:09:55,750 --> 00:09:56,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I've always been this way.</font>

155
00:09:57,190 --> 00:10:00,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Anyway, do you want to spar sometime?</font>

156
00:10:00,540 --> 00:10:02,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If you can last five minutes.</font>

157
00:10:02,780 --> 00:10:04,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Five minutes, huh?</font>

158
00:10:05,120 --> 00:10:09,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Judge's shop handles more 
valuable goods, doesn't it?</font>

159
00:10:09,650 --> 00:10:12,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Perhaps they avoided those because 
it would've been too obvious.</font>

160
00:10:12,290 --> 00:10:16,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They'd also get caught when 
they tried to sell them.</font>

161
00:10:16,330 --> 00:10:19,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm having my gang search 
the black market,</font>

162
00:10:19,330 --> 00:10:22,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and I haven't heard about any 
labyrinth goods on the market.</font>

163
00:10:23,160 --> 00:10:25,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I doubt they'll show up there.</font>

164
00:10:25,840 --> 00:10:28,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I thought you were staying out of this.</font>

165
00:10:28,130 --> 00:10:30,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I haven't done anything 
yet, so I'm still okay.</font>

166
00:10:30,490 --> 00:10:34,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Apparently he goes to the 
guild every day to complain.</font>

167
00:10:34,700 --> 00:10:36,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He's got more guts than I expected.</font>

168
00:10:39,540 --> 00:10:42,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Perhaps I'll take a job tomorrow.</font>

169
00:10:42,350 --> 00:10:43,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?</font>

170
00:10:43,110 --> 00:10:44,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm going with you!</font>

171
00:10:51,110 --> 00:10:53,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're taking that one?</font>

172
00:10:53,090 --> 00:10:54,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What do you think?</font>

173
00:10:54,240 --> 00:10:56,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Might be tough for you.</font>

174
00:10:56,050 --> 00:10:58,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Acquire white golem cores?</font>

175
00:10:58,980 --> 00:11:02,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Aren't golems resistant to magic?</font>

176
00:11:02,140 --> 00:11:04,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That'd be dangerous for you.</font>

177
00:11:04,260 --> 00:11:08,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But I've never seen a golem before.</font>

178
00:11:08,140 --> 00:11:09,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Suit yourself.</font>

179
00:11:10,180 --> 00:11:12,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Then I'll get this taken care of.</font>

180
00:11:19,540 --> 00:11:21,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't you think you're too soft on him?</font>

181
00:11:21,860 --> 00:11:26,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If he's going somewhere dangerous,
that means you'll have to protect him.</font>

182
00:11:26,400 --> 00:11:29,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't think that's a good 
way for a party to operate.</font>

183
00:11:29,720 --> 00:11:31,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How is that any of your business?</font>

184
00:11:31,940 --> 00:11:34,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It'll be my problem 
when I join the party.</font>

185
00:11:40,030 --> 00:11:41,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sorry.</font>

186
00:11:42,600 --> 00:11:46,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If he wanted me to protect him, he 
wouldn't take the job in the first place.</font>

187
00:11:46,630 --> 00:11:48,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But they're resistant to magic.</font>

188
00:11:49,240 --> 00:11:52,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He's serious about being an adventurer.</font>

189
00:11:56,050 --> 00:11:57,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thank you for waiting.</font>

190
00:11:57,670 --> 00:11:58,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Did something happen?</font>

191
00:11:58,950 --> 00:12:01,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I had a little request.</font>

192
00:12:06,810 --> 00:12:08,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What labyrinth are we going to?</font>

193
00:12:08,720 --> 00:12:14,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The closest labyrinth with white 
golems is... the Box Cavern?</font>

194
00:12:14,910 --> 00:12:15,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah.</font>

195
00:12:20,720 --> 00:12:24,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Adventurers generally 
stand out, don't they?</font>

196
00:12:24,150 --> 00:12:26,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's their weapons that stand out.</font>

197
00:12:26,340 --> 00:12:29,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And some of their armor looks awesome.</font>

198
00:12:29,080 --> 00:12:32,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They're unique. I enjoy looking at them.</font>

199
00:12:32,390 --> 00:12:35,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">People who really care about their 
appearance get them custom made.</font>

200
00:12:35,650 --> 00:12:38,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">With materials they've 
desperately gathered.</font>

201
00:12:38,650 --> 00:12:42,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Then they break what 
they ordered in a day.</font>

202
00:12:42,060 --> 00:12:43,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What a tough world we live in.</font>

203
00:12:44,470 --> 00:12:48,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But you guys wear practically 
only cloth armor.</font>

204
00:12:48,240 --> 00:12:50,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You must use a ton of nice materials.</font>

205
00:12:51,350 --> 00:12:53,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're lightly armored as well.</font>

206
00:12:53,990 --> 00:12:56,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I just don't like heavy stuff.</font>

207
00:12:56,780 --> 00:12:59,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I still take a lot of 
damage when I get hit.</font>

208
00:13:03,990 --> 00:13:06,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">All the way back, please.</font>

209
00:13:06,460 --> 00:13:08,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A little more.</font>

210
00:13:08,200 --> 00:13:10,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're really packing us in there.</font>

211
00:13:10,170 --> 00:13:13,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sorry. The inside's already full.</font>

212
00:13:15,990 --> 00:13:18,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is surprisingly unstable.</font>

213
00:13:18,260 --> 00:13:19,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, yeah.</font>

214
00:13:19,940 --> 00:13:22,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Doesn't your butt hurt?</font>

215
00:13:22,180 --> 00:13:25,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A little. Oh, right.</font>

216
00:13:27,290 --> 00:13:29,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Here, Gil.</font>

217
00:13:29,970 --> 00:13:31,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And for you as well.</font>

218
00:13:32,110 --> 00:13:34,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is this an illusion wolf pelt?</font>

219
00:13:34,590 --> 00:13:36,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And you used it to make a cushion?</font>

220
00:13:36,250 --> 00:13:38,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't like hard seats.</font>

221
00:13:38,070 --> 00:13:39,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I had it made.</font>

222
00:13:39,680 --> 00:13:41,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What a waste.</font>

223
00:13:43,750 --> 00:13:45,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's so fluffy!</font>

224
00:13:45,410 --> 00:13:46,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Isn't it?</font>

225
00:13:49,600 --> 00:13:52,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We'll be at the first labyrinth soon.</font>

226
00:13:52,260 --> 00:13:54,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We're going to the third, right?</font>

227
00:13:54,540 --> 00:13:55,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah.</font>

228
00:13:57,700 --> 00:13:58,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Gil?</font>

229
00:14:00,070 --> 00:14:03,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm impressed you noticed 
when you're not a beastman.</font>

230
00:14:07,830 --> 00:14:11,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Birds that run incredibly 
quickly along the ground.</font>

231
00:14:11,120 --> 00:14:13,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They have a mysterious intensity.</font>

232
00:14:13,770 --> 00:14:16,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They hardly fly even though they can.</font>

233
00:14:16,990 --> 00:14:19,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Maybe they run faster.</font>

234
00:14:19,510 --> 00:14:22,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Gil, catch me if I seem like I'll fall.</font>

235
00:14:22,650 --> 00:14:23,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Just don't.</font>

236
00:14:25,430 --> 00:14:27,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, it's the noble.</font>

237
00:14:27,460 --> 00:14:31,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Be careful. We nearly 
attacked you by accident.</font>

238
00:14:31,010 --> 00:14:32,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm sorry.</font>

239
00:14:32,310 --> 00:14:34,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So, are there monsters?</font>

240
00:14:34,230 --> 00:14:36,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes. Three forest runners.</font>

241
00:14:37,330 --> 00:14:38,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yikes.</font>

242
00:14:38,200 --> 00:14:40,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Their beaks really hurt.</font>

243
00:14:40,400 --> 00:14:44,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If there aren't any materials 
you'd like, I'll defeat them now.</font>

244
00:14:44,500 --> 00:14:46,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What? Uh, thanks.</font>

245
00:14:47,000 --> 00:14:48,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Do you want any materials?</font>

246
00:14:48,470 --> 00:14:49,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No, I'm good.</font>

247
00:14:52,210 --> 00:14:56,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, one got away. They really are fast.</font>

248
00:14:59,530 --> 00:15:00,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There.</font>

249
00:15:00,550 --> 00:15:02,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why's it floating?</font>

250
00:15:02,570 --> 00:15:04,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">To combat the recoil.</font>

251
00:15:04,120 --> 00:15:05,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let me see that again.</font>

252
00:15:06,320 --> 00:15:07,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No.</font>

253
00:15:10,400 --> 00:15:11,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's wrong?</font>

254
00:15:11,990 --> 00:15:13,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I feel sick.</font>

255
00:15:13,920 --> 00:15:15,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're motion sick?</font>

256
00:15:15,670 --> 00:15:17,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You were fine during the escort job.</font>

257
00:15:17,610 --> 00:15:20,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The wagon didn't shake 
this much last time.</font>

258
00:15:21,050 --> 00:15:22,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you okay?</font>

259
00:15:25,400 --> 00:15:28,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Chocolate? Thank you.</font>

260
00:15:28,060 --> 00:15:29,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Whoa.</font>

261
00:15:39,360 --> 00:15:41,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sweets are good for motion sickness.</font>

262
00:15:43,250 --> 00:15:45,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I think I feel a bit better.</font>

263
00:15:45,710 --> 00:15:47,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Then give me your hand.</font>

264
00:15:49,340 --> 00:15:52,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There's a pressure point here 
to stop motion sickness.</font>

265
00:15:52,300 --> 00:15:54,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I feel thoroughly pampered.</font>

266
00:15:54,370 --> 00:15:57,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well? Pretty useful, right?</font>

267
00:15:57,590 --> 00:16:00,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, you're a very good boy.</font>

268
00:16:06,150 --> 00:16:10,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The construction is rather 
precise. I like it.</font>

269
00:16:10,470 --> 00:16:11,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I know.</font>

270
00:16:11,480 --> 00:16:13,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's exactly like I imagined.</font>

271
00:16:14,800 --> 00:16:16,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There's a trap there.</font>

272
00:16:18,570 --> 00:16:19,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You mean this?</font>

273
00:16:20,830 --> 00:16:23,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?!</font>

274
00:16:23,730 --> 00:16:25,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why'd you step on it?!</font>

275
00:16:25,460 --> 00:16:28,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Didn't I tell you? I did, didn't I?</font>

276
00:16:28,070 --> 00:16:30,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I was curious what kind of trap 
it was and couldn't help it.</font>

277
00:16:30,300 --> 00:16:32,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Control yourself!</font>

278
00:16:32,130 --> 00:16:35,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Anyway, how did you 
know there was a trap?</font>

279
00:16:35,890 --> 00:16:39,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Instinct, I guess. More importantly...</font>

280
00:16:44,660 --> 00:16:46,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Mind if I handle this?</font>

281
00:16:46,390 --> 00:16:47,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Go ahead.</font>

282
00:16:50,090 --> 00:16:53,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He's unique, isn't he?</font>

283
00:16:53,120 --> 00:16:57,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Only the truly eccentric dual wield.</font>

284
00:16:59,980 --> 00:17:01,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Impressive.</font>

285
00:17:04,590 --> 00:17:08,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Am I underwhelming after 
seeing the Blade?</font>

286
00:17:08,480 --> 00:17:14,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No. To be honest, your flashy movements 
looked more impressive to me.</font>

287
00:17:14,790 --> 00:17:17,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah, they'd seem flashy when 
you're dodging that much.</font>

288
00:17:17,860 --> 00:17:21,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I just don't like getting hurt. 
And I like my style.</font>

289
00:17:21,780 --> 00:17:25,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can't help watching since 
dual wielders are unusual.</font>

290
00:17:25,440 --> 00:17:29,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's far more normal than your weapons.</font>

291
00:17:40,540 --> 00:17:42,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They're big.</font>

292
00:17:42,190 --> 00:17:45,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They're on the bigger side 
for a non-boss monster.</font>

293
00:17:45,770 --> 00:17:50,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They're slow, but they're resistant 
to magic and blades, too.</font>

294
00:17:50,850 --> 00:17:52,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let me try something.</font>

295
00:17:54,250 --> 00:17:56,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I told you, magic won't—</font>

296
00:17:57,590 --> 00:17:59,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How'd that pierce it?</font>

297
00:17:59,270 --> 00:18:04,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I read in the encyclopedia that golems 
are resistant to magic because their cores</font>

298
00:18:04,840 --> 00:18:06,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">absorb the mana of magical attacks.</font>

299
00:18:06,700 --> 00:18:08,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">An encyclopedia? How diligent.</font>

300
00:18:09,190 --> 00:18:11,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But my rifle...</font>

301
00:18:13,490 --> 00:18:15,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The mana's end point isn't the monster.</font>

302
00:18:15,870 --> 00:18:20,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It passes through instead, so I 
thought it might not be absorbed.</font>

303
00:18:22,620 --> 00:18:24,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Was your experiment successful?</font>

304
00:18:24,320 --> 00:18:25,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes.</font>

305
00:18:25,620 --> 00:18:27,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Then you've had your fun.</font>

306
00:18:27,880 --> 00:18:29,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm killing them.</font>

307
00:18:30,990 --> 00:18:33,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How'd you finish it off so quickly?!</font>

308
00:18:38,260 --> 00:18:40,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">These guys are unbelievable.</font>

309
00:18:49,920 --> 00:18:50,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Here.</font>

310
00:18:52,120 --> 00:18:53,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is this the core?</font>

311
00:18:53,950 --> 00:18:58,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What kind of freak stomps on 
a golem to break it down?</font>

312
00:18:58,340 --> 00:18:59,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Do mine, too.</font>

313
00:18:59,960 --> 00:19:01,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Do it yourself.</font>

314
00:19:01,410 --> 00:19:03,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll do it.</font>

315
00:19:03,590 --> 00:19:05,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Just wait there.</font>

316
00:19:05,000 --> 00:19:07,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Whatever. Let's head to the next place.</font>

317
00:19:09,200 --> 00:19:13,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's our job. Should we let him?</font>

318
00:19:13,590 --> 00:19:16,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let him do what he wants.</font>

319
00:19:17,560 --> 00:19:19,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We got so many.</font>

320
00:19:19,760 --> 00:19:21,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Too many.</font>

321
00:19:23,180 --> 00:19:27,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The next wagon's in... thirty minutes.</font>

322
00:19:27,390 --> 00:19:31,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It must be past noon. I'm hungry.</font>

323
00:19:32,680 --> 00:19:34,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Then you can have these.</font>

324
00:19:34,650 --> 00:19:36,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thank you.</font>

325
00:19:36,450 --> 00:19:37,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, Blade.</font>

326
00:19:38,260 --> 00:19:40,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We've got time. What do you say?</font>

327
00:19:45,800 --> 00:19:47,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You'd better last five minutes.</font>

328
00:19:47,900 --> 00:19:49,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nice.</font>

329
00:19:54,410 --> 00:19:55,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Give us a signal.</font>

330
00:19:56,470 --> 00:19:57,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Begin.</font>

331
00:20:02,690 --> 00:20:05,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How are you so quick 
with such a big sword?</font>

332
00:20:05,420 --> 00:20:08,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't aim for the neck. 
It makes it hard to hold back.</font>

333
00:20:11,710 --> 00:20:14,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>They're too fast for me to follow.</i></font>

334
00:20:17,400 --> 00:20:20,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We couldn't find our last marionette.</font>

335
00:20:21,400 --> 00:20:24,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Whoa, what is that?</font>

336
00:20:24,900 --> 00:20:29,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They're sparring. 
Excuse us for taking up space.</font>

337
00:20:32,000 --> 00:20:35,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's fine. Wait, is that the Blade?</font>

338
00:20:37,880 --> 00:20:40,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>This adventurer sure seems like a noble!</i></font>

339
00:20:41,610 --> 00:20:44,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You must be tired. Have some.</font>

340
00:20:44,370 --> 00:20:45,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Uh, thanks.</font>

341
00:20:48,160 --> 00:20:50,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That was dangerous.</font>

342
00:20:50,660 --> 00:20:53,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But I gave those to you!</font>

343
00:20:54,970 --> 00:20:57,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">As you can see, he's been scolded.</font>

344
00:20:57,300 --> 00:20:59,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Please forgive him.</font>

345
00:20:59,550 --> 00:21:02,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Here, to make up for it. 
We gathered plenty.</font>

346
00:21:02,060 --> 00:21:06,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What? These are the marionette 
ribbons we're looking for.</font>

347
00:21:06,790 --> 00:21:08,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I hope you'll forgive him now.</font>

348
00:21:08,840 --> 00:21:10,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Uh, sure.</font>

349
00:21:12,630 --> 00:21:18,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm not in your party. You 
don't have to protect me.</font>

350
00:21:18,580 --> 00:21:20,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's my fault.</font>

351
00:21:20,350 --> 00:21:24,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It was rude of me to share 
when you gave them to me.</font>

352
00:21:30,060 --> 00:21:32,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We'll eat them together, okay?</font>

353
00:21:41,520 --> 00:21:43,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He lasted five minutes.</font>

354
00:21:43,580 --> 00:21:46,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And could apparently afford 
to pay attention to you.</font>

355
00:21:53,120 --> 00:21:55,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, the wagon is here.</font>

356
00:21:56,110 --> 00:21:58,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Come on, let's go.</font>

357
00:22:06,410 --> 00:22:07,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah, yeah.</font>

358
00:23:39,970 --> 00:23:44,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<font face="Times New Roman"><font color="#16191b">Next Time</font></font></font>

